1:\"WordPress 4.9 kalean!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2017/11/16/wordpress-4-9-kalean/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2017/11/16/wordpress-4-9-kalean/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 16 Nov 2017 13:45:29 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Albistea\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/?p=301\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"Prest dago jada WordPress-en 4.9 bertsioa eta oraingoan ere euskaraz hasiera-hasieratik!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"IkusiMakusi\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1636:\"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/11/wp49.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-304\" src=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/11/wp49-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"692\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/11/wp49-1024x512.png 1024w, https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/11/wp49-300x150.png 300w, https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/11/wp49-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 692px) 100vw, 692px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Prest dago jada WordPress-en 4.9 bertsioa eta oraingoan ere euskaraz hasiera-hasieratik!</p>\n<p><strong>&#8220;Tipton&#8221;</strong> izena duen bertsio honek <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2017/11/tipton/\">hainbat berrikuntza dakartza</a>: <strong>pertsonalizatzailearen lan-fluxua hobetua, hobekuntzak kodean, widgeten are eguneraketa gehiago, guneak eraikitzeko hobekuntzak&#8230;</strong> Eskuragarri dituzu <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Version_4.9\">azalpen teknikoak</a> ere.</p>\n<p>Eguneratu zure WordPress instalazioa azken bertsio honetara edo <a href=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/release-archive/eu/wordpress-4.9-eu.zip\">deskargatu</a> hemendik!</p>\n<p>Itzulpenetan laguntza beti da ongi etorria, noski. WordPress euskaratzen lagundu nahi baduzu, eman izena <a href=\"http://librezale.eus/wiki/Posta-zerrendak\">Librezaleko posta zerrendan</a>, handik kudeatzen baita WordPress-en itzulpena (<a href=\"https://telegram.me/librezale\">Telegram talde bat</a> ere badugu). Eta besterik gabe, hasi WordPresseko nukleoa, itxurak edo pluginak euskaratzen <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/eu\">WordPress-en itzulpen zentroan</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2017/11/16/wordpress-4-9-kalean/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress 4.8 kalean!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2017/06/09/wordpress-4-8-kalean/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2017/06/09/wordpress-4-8-kalean/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Jun 2017 12:57:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Albistea\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/?p=287\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:494:\"Prest dago jada WordPress-en 4.8 bertsioa eta oraingoan ere euskaraz hasiera-hasieratik! &#8220;Evans&#8221; izena duen bertsio honek hainbat berrikuntza dakartza: widget eguneraketa zirraragarriak, esteketan hobekuntzak, laster zungandik gertu WordPressen inguruan egingo diren ekitaldiak&#8230; Eskuragarri dituzu azalpen teknikoak ere. Eguneratu zure WordPress instalazioa azken bertsio honetara edo deskargatu hemendik! Itzulpenetan laguntza beti da ongi etorria, noski. WordPress [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"IkusiMakusi\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2265:\"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-promotion-graphic.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-291 size-large\" src=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-promotion-graphic-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"692\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-promotion-graphic-1024x512.png 1024w, https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-promotion-graphic-300x150.png 300w, https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-promotion-graphic-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 692px) 100vw, 692px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Prest dago jada WordPress-en 4.8 bertsioa eta oraingoan ere euskaraz hasiera-hasieratik!</p>\n<p><strong>&#8220;Evans&#8221;</strong> izena duen bertsio honek <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2017/06/evans/\">hainbat berrikuntza dakartza</a>: <strong>widget eguneraketa zirraragarriak, esteketan hobekuntzak, laster zungandik gertu WordPressen inguruan egingo diren ekitaldiak&#8230;</strong> Eskuragarri dituzu <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Version_4.8\">azalpen teknikoak</a> ere.</p>\n<p>Eguneratu zure WordPress instalazioa azken bertsio honetara edo <a href=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/release-archive/eu/wordpress-4.8-eu.zip\">deskargatu</a> hemendik!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-banner.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-293\" src=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-banner-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"692\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-banner-1024x512.png 1024w, https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-banner-300x150.png 300w, https://eu.wordpress.org/files/2017/06/release-banner-768x384.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 692px) 100vw, 692px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Itzulpenetan laguntza beti da ongi etorria, noski. WordPress euskaratzen lagundu nahi baduzu, eman izena <a href=\"http://librezale.eus/wiki/Posta-zerrendak\">Librezaleko posta zerrendan</a>, handik kudeatzen baita WordPress-en itzulpena (<a href=\"https://telegram.me/librezale\">Telegram talde bat</a> ere badugu). Eta besterik gabe, hasi WordPress-eko nukleoa, itxurak edo pluginak euskaratzen <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/eu\">WordPress-en itzulpen zentroan</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2017/06/09/wordpress-4-8-kalean/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress 4.7 kalean!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://eu.wordpress.org/2016/12/06/wordpress-4-7-kalean/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\